Hello! My name is Sarah, and I’m with RT 6 Boozers, your go-to bar for great drinks and good vibes. How can I assist you today?

Hi Sarah! I'm just wondering about your happy hour specials.

We have amazing happy hour specials from four o'clock to six o'clock every weekday. May I ask for your name so I can assist you better?

Sure, my name is John.

Great to meet you, John! To help you with our offers, could you please provide me with your email address?

Sure, it's johnsmith@gmail.com.

Thank you, John! And could you also confirm your birth year for our records? Just the year is fine.

I was born in nineteen eighty-five.

Thank you for that information, John! I appreciate it. Is there anything else I can help you with regarding our menu or events?

Not at the moment. I think I have all the information I need.

Alright! Thank you for your time, John. If you have any more questions, feel free to reach out. Have a fantastic day!
